{"type": "article", "id": 29823, "title": "便携烧烤架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-19T23:03:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160719165202qVcU85SrYQZtEO7h.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>与朋友在一起 BBQ 就好像是生活的佐料，为了让人们不受限制更好地享受美妙的聚会时光，<a href=\"http://www.formaxiom.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">formAxiom</a> 采用了富有新意的伞状折叠法，设计了一款便携烧烤架 <a href=\"http://www.formaxiom.com/grillo-the-barbecue/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grillo</a>。修长的架身由不锈钢制作而成，三个立足点即便是在凹凸不平的表面也能牢固竖立，使用时只需要把它像伞一样撑开即可，不需要做其他组装步骤。展开后的烧烤架还附带了一个环状网结构的不锈钢吊床，适用于任何固体燃料，材质的透气性能够保证火焰能在短时间内提供较强的热量，而分叉的三脚结构依然能保持不烫手的状态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719170354JlBY1y6VX0wqsDFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719170354y36Vg85oGTlMpwmF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719170354jxP3MKVGOi7tfpEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.135697\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719170354Zwst7amiWKzRlYxH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.135697\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}